member.name: T:MyDeque`1

member.name: M:MyDeque`1.Count
member.summary: returns the number of elements in the Deque

member.name: M:MyDeque`1.PushLast(`0)
member.summary: inserts element at the end of the Deque

member.name: M:MyDeque`1.PushFirst(`0)
member.summary: inserts element at the beginning of the Deque

member.name: M:MyDeque`1.PopLast
member.summary: removes and returns the element at the end of the Deque

member.name: M:MyDeque`1.PopFirst
member.summary: removes and returns the element at the beginning of the Deque

member.name: M:MyDeque`1.PeekLast
member.summary: returns the element at the end of the Deque without removing it

member.name: M:MyDeque`1.PeekFirst

member.name: M:MyDeque`1.Clear
